&lt;li&gt;Strong operator and troubleshooting skills for elctro-opto-mechanical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious about customer applications and able to understand their technical challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with a contemporary programming language (such as Python) is highly desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communicator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-driven and thrive in an environment of high-performance expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willing to travel up to 70%; primarily within the US/Canada and occasionally internationally.&lt;/li&gt;
